title: Trump Has 'Positive Call' With Russia's Putin After Zelenskiy Meeting
description: The White House says President Donald Trump had a "positive call" with Russian President Vladimir Putin after meeting with Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskiy in Florida on Sunday. Bloomberg's Tyler Kendall reports.  (Source: Bloomberg)
